= SDL_GetModState =

Get the current key modifier state for the keyboard.

== Syntax ==

<syntaxhighlight lang='c'>
SDL_Keymod SDL_GetModState(void);
</syntaxhighlight>

== Return Value ==

Returns an OR'd combination of the modifier keys for the keyboard. See
[[SDL_Keymod]] for details.



